      <section id="how-to-apply">
        <h2>How to Build a Behavior Change That Lasts</h2>
        <p>
          The following framework integrates the research findings into a practical sequence for building durable behavior change. It is designed to work with human psychology rather than against it — replacing willpower-dependent strategies with structural, identity-based, and environmentally-supported approaches.
        </p>

        <StepsList steps={[
